cast.overview: An aging Chinese immigrant is swept up in an insane adventure, where she alone can save what's important to her by connecting with the lives she could have led in other universes.
cast.title: Everything Everywhere All at Once

details.biography: Tallie Medel is an American actress, writer, dancer, choreographer, and comedienne, best known for her work in independent films. They graduated from Emerson College, Boston, MA, in 2008 with a degree in Acting and Theater Education, and is a co-founder of dance-comedy trio Cocoon Central Dance Team alongside Sunita Mani and Eleanore Pienta.
details.name: Tallie Medel
